iaik.x509.ocsp.extensions

Class PreferredSignatureAlgorithms.PreferredSignatureAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.x509.ocsp.extensions.PreferredSignatureAlgorithms.PreferredSignatureAlgorithm
  • Enclosing class:
    PreferredSignatureAlgorithms

    public static final class PreferredSignatureAlgorithms.PreferredSignatureAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the PreferredSignatureAlgorithm component of the OCSP PrefferedSignatureAlgorithms extension.
    A PreferredSignatureAlgorithm specifies the preferred signature algorithm and (optionally) the public key algorithm identifier the client prefers in the responder certificate.

      • decode

        public void decode(ASN1Object asn1Obj)
            throws CodingException
        Decodes this PreferredSignatureAlgorithm from its ASN.1 representation.

        A PreferredSignatureAlgorithm specifies the preferred signature algorithm and (optionally) the public key algorithm identifier the client prefers in the responder certificate: 

        
 PreferredSignatureAlgorithm ::= SEQUENCE {
    sigIdentifier        AlgorithmIdentifier,
    pubKeyAlgIdentifier  SMIMECapability OPTIONAL
    }
        Parameters:
        asn1Obj - the ASN.1 representation of the PreferredSignatureAlgorithm
        Throws:
        CodingException - if the ASN1Object could not be parsed
